- [ ] Is the app running?
  - [ ] If not, display a message to the user and link to the install page
- [ ] If so, display:
  - [ ] Current status
  - [ ] Pause option
  - [ ] Override option
  - [ ] Configuration option
- [ ] Pause option
  - [ ] 5 minute increments, stopping with 30m
  - [ ] Not available if already paused
- [ ] Override option
  - [ ] Always available
  - [ ] Choose from a list of options
  - [ ] Choose activation time
- [ ] Configuration
  - [ ] Opens config JSON in a text editor